data.description: Welcome to your rural oasis at 388 Calaveras Rd, Pinon Hills! Nestled on almost 2 acres of land, this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers a serene retreat just a minute away from Highway 138. As you arrive, an electric gate gracefully welcomes you to this well-maintained property, providing a sense of security and seclusion. The home has an open floor plan, offering a seamless flow between the spacious living areas, perfect for both relaxation and entertaining guests. The kitchen has sleek countertops and gleaming stainless steel appliances, providing durability and a modern aesthetic. The breakfast bar becomes an inviting space for casual dining or social gatherings. The interior of the bedrooms have walk-in closets, enhancing storage space and organization. Some interior amenities include a convenient indoor laundry room and a thoughtfully designed split floor plan, enhancing the functionality and privacy of the home. This property features a two-car garage, ideal for additional storage space. The front of the home is landscaped with mature trees and has a drip system. Don't miss the chance to make this peaceful retreat your own!
